item.title: 【SD Live Performances】PACK - Céline Dion - BST Hyde Park 2019 (Pro-Shot YTDL) [Quality may vary and updated every week]
item.description:
Hello there!
It's a pleasure to meet you at my new account in ShareMania.US.
(Known as @jamieses)


As I suppose you already know, there are recent surface leaks on YouTube this month. And fortunately, it's a good leak: Céline Dion's memorable show at BST Hyde Park, 5th July 2019. Actually, it was pretty clear that this show was going to be leaked, and here we are. Last year, we were surprised to see a pristine-quality pro shot of "My Heart Will Go On" by Fandefan. My team are searching for the source of these leaks, and the information that we have now is that this recent May leak has as a source one MP4 file. I don't know the quality yet, but apparently it is about 01 hour and 50 minutes long (approximately). This upload contains the leak of "My Heart Will Go On" and the recent leaks "You're The Voice", "Think Twice" and "Imagine". Updated every week, so keep looking forward to the new leak. Making this because if the leak channel on YouTube got down all of sudden, we would have a backup of this beautiful majestic concert. Here you go:
